The project was done to classify fraudulent credit card transaction from normal transactions. 
The following project makes use of scikit-learn and pandas library in python
Used logistic regression to differentiate the fraudulent transaction from the normal ones.
The model is under-sampled randomly, hence the accuracy for each the program runs will be different in the case of training and test.
The data used in this project is obtained from Kaggle. None of the data belongs to the code owner. 
